= Email Setup <sup>[[Help:Configuration |<img width="19" src="../images/navigation/help_start.png" />]]</sup>=
On this page you can enable, set up, configure and test the Email functionality. 
== Basic ==
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.admin.InlineConfigurationWidget 
 | fields = {{   'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
 | configOptions = {{ 'emailUser' | 'emailPwd' | 'mail.smtp.host' | 'mail.smtp.port' | 'mail.smtp.sourceaddress'}}
}}

== Advanced ==
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.admin.InlineConfigurationWidget 
 | fields = {{   'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
 | configOptions = {{ 'mail.smtp.auth' | 'mail.smtp.connectiontimeout' | 'mail.smtp.starttls.enable' | 'mail.smtp.timeout' | 'mail.transport.protocol' | 'maxContextItems' | 'sendEmailsForEachEvent' | 'serverUrl' | 'useSSLforSMTP' }}
}}

== Activate Email ==

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.admin.InlineConfigurationWidget 
 | fields = {{   'PROPERTY_NAME' | 'INPUT_FIELD' | 'DESCRIPTION' }}
 | configOptions = {{ 'sendEmails' }}
}}

== Test Email Settings==
{{#widget: CodeExecution
 | userInput = {{ 
      {{ name = 'targetEmail'
       | required = true
       | displayName = 'Target Email Address'
       | componentType = 'SIMPLE'
      }} }}
 | args = {{ $this$ | '%targetEmail' }}
 | method = 'sendTestMail'
 | label = 'Send testmail'
 | clazz = 'com.fluidops.iwb.util.EmailTest'
}}